class ListNode:

    def __init__(self, val=1, next=None):
        self.val = val
        self.next = next

def swapNodes(head, pos1, pos2):
    dummy = ListNode(0)
    dummy.next = head
    (prev1, prev2) = (dummy, dummy)
    for _ in range(pos1 - 1):
        prev1 = prev1.next
    for _ in range(pos2 - 1):
        prev2 = prev2.next
    node1 = prev1.next
    node2 = prev2.next
    prev1.next = node2
    prev2.next = node1
    (node1.next, node2.next) = (node2.next, node1.next)
    return dummy.next
